OL,3,CRailway worker knocked down by train
OL,4,Ctravelling too fast, report finds
OL,6,FGreat Western Railway failed to
OL,7,Fcontrol risks when a worker was hit by
OL,8,Fa train at a depot in Bristol, a
OL,9,Freport has found.
OL,11,FThey were seriously injured at the St
OL,12,FPhilip's Marsh depot in September 2023.
OL,14,FA report by the Rail Accidents
OL,15,FInvestigation Branch said that trains
OL,16,Fthere were exceeding the speed limit.
