OL,3,CRailway worker knocked down by train
OL,4,Ctravelling too fast, report finds
OL,6,FAt around 1pm on 26 September 2023, a
OL,7,Fmember of staff responsible for
OL,8,Fshunting the trains was struck by one
OL,9,Fthat was leaving the main shed.
OL,11,FIt was travelling at 10mph at the
OL,12,Ftime, the RAIB said.
OL,14,FAfter hearing the train hit something,
OL,15,Fthe driver stopped.
OL,17,FOthers working nearby saw that the
OL,18,Fshunter was lying next to the train
OL,19,Fand went to help them.
