OL,3,CRailway worker knocked down by train
OL,4,Ctravelling too fast, report finds
OL,6,FAfter exiting the main shed building
OL,7,Fvia a roller shutter door, the shunter
OL,8,Fhad walked into the path of a train.
OL,10,FIts driver had then started to move it
OL,11,Fand accelerate much quicker than the
OL,12,Fshunter expected.
OL,14,FThe shunter took this route to get to
OL,15,Fa level crossing that ran across the
OL,16,Fend of the shed building.
OL,18,FAccording to the report, the shunter
OL,19,Fdid this because they wanted to check
OL,20,Fthat no one was approaching the level
OL,21,Fcrossing from a blind corner.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
