OL,3,CRailway worker knocked down by train
OL,4,Ctravelling too fast, report finds
OL,6,FThe shunter regularly used the area
OL,7,Fbetween the main shed building and the
OL,8,Flevel crossing as a walking route, so
OL,9,Fwas used to being there.
OL,11,FHowever, by using this route the
OL,12,Fshunter had to walk close to or foul
OL,13,Fof the train's path.
OL,15,FThe shunter was also unaware that the
OL,16,Ftrain had started to move and did not
OL,17,Frealise it was catching up with them.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
