OL,3,CRailway worker knocked down by train
OL,4,Ctravelling too fast, report finds
OL,6,FThey had expected to reach the level
OL,7,Fcrossing before the train, but the
OL,8,Ftrain exceeded the speed limit of 5mph
OL,9,For 8 kmh.
OL,11,FThe driver did not observe the shunter
OL,12,Fwalking ahead of the train so did not
OL,13,Ftake any appropriate actions in
OL,14,Fresponse.
OL,16,FThe shunter, who had sustained serious
OL,17,Finjuries, was treated by paramedics
OL,18,Fand then taken to hospital.
OL,20,FGWR response
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
