OL,3,CRailway worker knocked down by train
OL,4,Ctravelling too fast, report finds
OL,6,FThe RAIB found that an underlying
OL,7,Ffactor was that GWR had not
OL,8,Feffectively controlled the risk of a
OL,9,Fshunter being struck by a train
OL,10,Foutside a shed building.
OL,12,FGWR's assurance processes also had not
OL,13,Fidentified that train movements within
OL,14,Fthe depot were exceeding the speed
OL,15,Flimit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
