OL,3,CRailway worker knocked down by train
OL,4,Ctravelling too fast, report finds
OL,6,FFollowing the accident, GWR updated
OL,7,Fits risk assessment and introduced new
OL,8,Fcontrol measures to specifically
OL,9,Fmanage the risks to staff associated
OL,10,Fwith trains moving outside the main
OL,11,Fshed building.
OL,13,FGWR also addressed the deficiencies
OL,14,Ffound with its assurance processes for
OL,15,Fmonitoring if drivers were complying
OL,16,Fwith the speed limits on its depots.
OL,18,FA GWR spokesperson said: "We recognise
OL,19,Fthat this was a very serious incident
OL,20,Fto a member of our team.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
