OL,3,CRailway worker knocked down by train
OL,4,Ctravelling too fast, report finds
OL,6,F"We have conducted a thorough review
OL,7,Fof our risk mitigations; identified
OL,8,Foptions to reduce those risks, and
OL,9,Fcontinue the work of implementation.
OL,11,F"This includes addressing the
OL,12,Frecommendations made by the RAIB to
OL,13,Freview personal track safety
OL,14,Fcertification standards and walking
OL,15,Froutes at our depots.
OL,17,F"The safety of our colleagues and our
OL,18,Fpassengers is our highest priority."
